YOU HEUNG, Appellant, v. UNITED STATES, Appellee. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. November 4, 1929. No. 5805. Frank J. Hennessy, of San Francisco, Cal., for appellant. George J. Hatfield, U. S. Atty., and Lucas E. Kilkenny, Asst. U. S. Atty., both of San Francisco, Cal.

Before BUDKIN, DIETBICH, and WlLBUE, Circuit Judges.

DIETRICH, Circuit Judge.

The record in this ease is in every material respect identical with that considered in No. 5804, Wong Hop v. United States (C. C. A.) 35 F.(2d) 596, this day decided, and herein the same direction is given to the court below as was given in that ease.
